
task build-gyroscope
  base options

  call make
    bind constructor, text <Gyroscope>
    bind factor, link options
    turn seed

task get-x
  base build

  cause get-aspect
    bind object, link build
    bind aspect, text <x>
    turn seed

task get-y
  base build

  cause get-aspect
    bind object, link build
    bind aspect, text <y>
    turn seed

task get-z
  base build

  cause get-aspect
    bind object, link build
    bind aspect, text <z>
    turn seed
